{"tid":600320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"四太千金超盈超欣 13億豪宅租值升一成 勁過李澤楷","createTime":"2018-03-21T08:00:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T06:47:05.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fb1fd6f06051e18cc0aa50b2e0ad6c5670c5bbc9","tid":600320,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T08:00:38.000Z","msg":"賭王何鴻燊四太梁安琪，兩年前一句「想小朋友學投資」，就一擲近13億元協助兩位「90後」千金掃入山頂豪宅Mount Nicholson分層單位，包括何超欣持有的9樓A及B室，以及何超盈持有的10樓A及B室，按今日差估署最新租值，她們購入的4伙單位，租值按年升一成。<br />\n<br />\n2017至18年度，9樓A及B室租值分別515.4萬及472.68萬元，最新租值升10%至分別567萬及519.96萬元，即兩伙租值每年達1,086.96萬元，以購入價6.464億元計算，租金回報率1.7厘。10樓A及B室，2017至18年度租值分別529.8萬及486.24萬元，最新一年度租值，分別上升至582.72萬及534.84萬元，兩伙全年租值1,117.56萬元，以購入價6.446億元計算，租金回報率1.7厘。<br />\n相反，不少富豪持有大宅，租值未見上升。李澤楷於石澳大浪灣道12號，2018至19年租值維持565.56萬元，<br />\n恒大許家印的山頂布力徑10號C屋，最新租值維持557.4萬元，相比下，何超盈持有的Mount Nicholsin 10樓A室，一年租值582.72萬元，比李澤楷及許家印大宅還要高。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180319/large/1521444204_edcf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180319%2Flarge%2F1521444204_edcf.jpg&h=1fde99f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180319/57967281\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180319%2F57967281&d=WqTtVrWfq%2BIAU1dwJNkwQW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=f89342b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180319%2F57967281&h=883b661f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180319/57967281</a>"},{"pid":"ecfc84b280073d76871d224cdf1b7c99057d28df","tid":600320,"uid":2429,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T08:01:29.000Z","msg":"收唔收男寵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78cbf4cf5c3370b5c6b0f8d8d5628829dcc9c1d7